commit.message:
Add description to have_received matcher

Evidently, a description method is needed in certain cases in RSpec.
This change fixes that issue.
Remove ##### comments where only a single class was in a file.

Move CompositeExpectation into its own file.

And add copyright notice to expectation builder.
Move ExpectationRecorder into its own file.
Convert method name to string for matching.
Allow partial mocks in demeter chain.

Working demeter mocking with partials.

Yay!
Make failing tests as pending for now.

Partially working demeter chain refactoring.

Demeter chains starting with a Partial mock seem to fail because the
partial never sees the initial mock (only the actual mock gets it).
Move CallRecord into its own file.

Removed rails view mocking.

This is fragile, complex, undocumented and hopefully unused.
It's gone now.
General improvement of the partial mock class.
Test that removing @flexmock_proxy cause particular error
Move call validation for spies into separate class.
